COCKtail Contest (04/13/2026)

The player with the most points starts as the Guesser, followed by the player with the second most points.

The Guesser is banished to a seperate room while the mixer is choosen and the drink is made.

The mixer is choosen randomly by spin the bottle. The mixer creates a cocktail that they themselfs would like to drink.

The Guesser then trys the drink and attempts to determine who the mixer is. The Guesser has 3 guesses. If guessed correctly on the:
    1rst Guess => 3pts
    2nd Guess => 2pts
    3rd Guess => 1pt

If the Guesser fails to identify the mixer they must finish the cocktail. If they do identify the mixer, then the mixer must finish the drink.

Winner is determined by most points won during the phase!